item.title: Week #1
item.description: To help myself get blogging in a regular routine, I’ve decided to do a weekly post at the end of each week, about my week, in retrospect. Today’s post will be post number one. A Fresh Start It might have been the week before, but I’ve restarted my iOS learning journey with this book (and Programming iOS 13, which follows it). Previously (~3 years back), I’d done a hands-on course on Udemy while I was still in college.
